{"type": "article", "id": 30482, "title": "源自经典作品的茶叶包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-02T23:04:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160802230526xPN6J9L4b7sVaIXd.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>从书架上取下一“本”《战争与桃子》（War and Peach）或者《唐·吉诃茶》（Don QuixoTea），用里面的茶叶泡上一杯茶——这个充满了文学作品梗的创意茶叶系列自去年在 Kickstarter 上线之后就利用它的复古风和幽默感迅速筹集到了足够的资金，推出了三款以经典小说“改编版”作为铁盒包装的茶叶。今年脑洞大开的设计师们邀请三位画家绘制了全新的英国系列，抹茶、柠檬和胡椒薄荷三款茶叶包装分别对莎翁的《无事生非》、狄更斯的《雾都孤儿》以及《傲慢与偏见》进行了独特的致敬。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1559433165/noveltea-tins-the-british-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，单盒的早鸟价为 25 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160802233105GBYTNvuiyZFx4s91.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562903\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160802233105gXFhAjLBMiCOtU2s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608022331055lpYvbzZK7UWDw4h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.645588\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px; height: 241px; width: 375px; left: 521px; top: 1522px;\" class=\"dragged\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160802233105KFToMAqNUZaOyI0g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div>"}